<main class="container">
  <a href="<%= books_path %>" class="general-back-link">
    <i class="fa fa-long-arrow-left mr-15"></i>Back to results</a>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-6">
      <div class="product-gallery">
        <div class="mb-20">
          <img src="https://www.bramstein.com/static/smashing-book-5-photo-stack.9d5d114e3e.jpg" class="img-responsive"/></div>
        <div class="images clearfix">
          <a href="#" class="img-link">
            <img src="https://www.smashingmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/smashing-book-5-2-large.jpg"/></a>
          <a href="#" class="img-link">
            <img src="https://www.smashingmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/smashing-book-5-2-large.jpg"/></a>
          <a href="#" class="img-link">
            <img src="https://www.smashingmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/smashing-book-5-2-large.jpg"/></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-6">
      <h1 class="mt-res-0"><%= @book.title %></h1>
      <p class="lead small">Vitaly Friedman, Daniel Mall,Vitaly Friedman</p>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
          <p class="h1 in-gold-500 mt-10">€<%= @book.price %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-5 col-md-3">
          <div class="input-group general-position">
            <a href="#" class="input-link">
              <i class="fa fa-minus line-height-40"></i>
            </a>
            <input type="text" class="form-control quantity-input"/>
            <a href="#" class="input-link">
              <i class="fa fa-plus line-height-40"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-7 col-md-5">
          <button class="btn btn-default pull-right general-position">Add to Cart</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="general-info-wrap divider-lg">
        <p>Description</p>
        <p class="lead small line-height-2"><%= @book.description %>
          <a href="#" class="in-gold-500 ml-10">Read More</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="general-info-wrap divider-lg">
        <div class="clearfix">
          <p class="pull-left">Year of publication</p>
          <p class="lead small pull-right"><%= @book.year %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="general-info-wrap divider-lg">
        <div class="clearfix">
          <p class="pull-left">Dimensions</p>
          <p class="lead small pull-right">H:<%= @book.dimension_h %>" x W: <%= @book.dimension_w %>" x D: <%= @book.dimension_d %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="general-info-wrap divider-lg">
        <div class="clearfix">
          <p class="pull-left">Materials</p>
          <p class="lead small pull-right"><%= @book.material %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mb-80">
    <h3>Write a Review</h3>
    <p class="general-info-text">Score</p>
    <div class="mb-15">
      <i class="fa fa-star rate-empty"></i>
      <i class="fa fa-star rate-empty"></i>
      <i class="fa fa-star rate-empty"></i>
      <i class="fa fa-star rate-empty"></i>
      <i class="fa fa-star rate-empty"></i>
    </div>
    <form class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <div class="mb-40">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="title" class="control-label input-label in-grey-600">Title</label>
            <input id="title" name="title" type="text" class="form-control"/></div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="review" class="control-label input-label in-grey-600">Review</label>
            <textarea id="review" name="review" type="text" class="form-control"></textarea>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-right">
          <button class="btn disabled mb-20">Post</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
  <div class="mb-80">
    <h3 class="in-gold-500 mb-25">Reviews (3)</h3>
    <div class="general-message-wrap divider-lg">
      <div class="clearfix">
        <img src="https://www.smashingmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/smashing-book-5-2-large.jpg" class="img-circle logo-size inlide-block pull-left"/>
        <div class="ml-70">
          <div>
            <div class="general-message-date hidden-xs">11/11/16</div>
            <div class="max-240">
              <div class="general-message-verified">Verified Reviewer</div>
              <div class="general-message-name">Rita J. Lewis</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-15">
            <i class="fa fa-star rate-star"></i>
            <i class="fa fa-star rate-star"></i>
            <i class="fa fa-star rate-star"></i>
            <i class="fa fa-star rate-star"></i>
            <i class="fa fa-star rate-star"></i>
          </div>
          <p>Thank you BookStore, I was very pleased to receive my order for the Moleskine diary so soon after placing the order.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="general-message-wrap divider-lg">
      <div class="clearfix">
        <span class="img-circle logo-size inlide-block pull-left logo-empty">M</span>
        <div class="ml-70">
          <div>
            <div class="general-message-date hidden-xs">11/11/16</div>
            <div class="max-240">
              <div class="general-message-verified pull-right">Verified Reviewer</div>
              <div class="general-message-name">May J. Novoa</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-15">
            <i class="fa fa-star rate-star"></i>
            <i class="fa fa-star rate-star"></i>
            <i class="fa fa-star rate-star"></i>
            <i class="fa fa-star rate-star"></i>
            <i class="fa fa-star rate-star rate-empty"></i>
          </div>
          <p>If ‘Get a better job’ had landed on my desk a year ago, I might have been dismissive of it. Instead I was prepared to be open-minded. There have been many occasions where I turned to career books with practical activities to look for some
            inspiration when developing education activities for learners or assessment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
